Kylie Jenner and Travis Scott spotted around Houston during Astroworld Fest weekend

In this combination photo, TV personality Kylie Jenner, left, attends Harper's Bazaar Icons celebration on Sept. 9, 2016, in New York and rapper Travis Scott performs at the 2017 iHeartRadio Music Festival on Sept. 23, 2017, in Las Vegas. In an Instagram post Sunday, Feb. 4, Jenner announced the birth of her baby girl born Thursday. It’s the first child for the 20-year-old reality star and the 25-year-old rapper. (Photos by Andy Kropa, left, and John Salangsang/Invision/AP) less In this combination photo, TV personality Kylie Jenner, left, attends Harper's Bazaar Icons celebration on Sept. 9, 2016, in New York and rapper Travis Scott performs at the 2017 iHeartRadio Music Festival on ... more Photo: Associated Press Photo: Associated Press Image 1 of / 20 Caption Close Kylie Jenner and Travis Scott spotted around Houston during Astroworld Fest weekend 1 / 20 Back to Gallery

Reality TV star and makeup mogul Kylie Jenner and her significant other Travis Scott hit Houston over the weekend for Scott's Astroworld Festival.

While the couple was in Houston, they made time in their busy schedules for more than just the Fest.

RELATED: Where in the world is Kylie Jenner? Houston, we think

Via social media Saturday, Scott announced the opening of his new retail store in Rice Village in January. On Sunday, the Missouri City native was honored with a city proclamation by Mayor Sylvester Turner.

Meanwhile, Jenner's makeup line launched at Ulta Beauty Stores across the nation on Saturday. On Sunday, she hit a local Ulta store at 5140 Richmond Avenue to celebrate and greet hundreds of fans.

Click through the photos above to see Kylie Jenner and Travis Scott's weekend in Houston, outside of Astroworld Festival.
